{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idbd7622a0-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s6250"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"6250"},"text":"§ 6250.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Establishment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idbd7622a1-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s6250/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Notwithstanding any other provision of this chapter, the Secretary may establish, maintain, and operate in the Northeast a Northeast Home Heating Oil Reserve. A Reserve established under this part is not a component of the Strategic Petroleum Reserve established under part B of this subchapter. A Reserve established under this part shall contain no more than 2 million barrels of petroleum distillate.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idbd7622a2-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s6250/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" For the purposes of this part—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbd7622a3-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s6250/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the term “Northeast” means the States of Maine, New Hampshire, Vermont, Massachusetts, Connecticut, Rhode Island, New York, Pennsylvania, and New Jersey;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbd7622a4-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s6250/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the term “petroleum distillate” includes heating oil and diesel fuel; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbd7622a5-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s6250/b/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the term “Reserve” means the Northeast Home Heating Oil Reserve established under this part.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idbd7622a6-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/163/tI/s181"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–163, title I, § 181","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/469/tII/s201/a/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–469, title II, § 201(a)(3)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2000-11-09"},"text":"Nov. 9, 2000","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/114/2034"},"text":"114 Stat. 2034","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idbd7622a7-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idbd7622a8-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idbd7622a9-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This chapter, referred to in subsec. (a), was in the original “this Act”, meaning ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/163"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–163","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1975-12-22"},"text":"Dec. 22, 1975","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/89/871"},"text":"89 Stat. 871","children":[],"tail":", known as the Energy Policy and Conservation Act. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s6201"},"text":"section 6201 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"priorProvisions","id":"idbd7622aa-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Prior Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"A prior ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/163/s181"},"text":"section 181 of Pub. L. 94–163","children":[],"tail":" was renumbered section 191 and was classified to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s6251"},"text":"section 6251 of this title","children":[],"tail":", prior to repeal by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/58"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–58","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
